OL,6,FClaire Barrow, of the Environment
OL,7,FAgency, said: "Our climate is
OL,8,Fchanging, and we had 22 days of almost
OL,9,Fno recorded rainfall in May.
OL,11,F"While we have had some rain at the
OL,12,Fstart of June, it has not been enough
OL,13,Fto reverse the impacts of the
OL,14,Fprolonged dry weather.
