OL,6,F"We are working with Yorkshire Water
OL,7,Fto make sure they enact their drought
OL,8,Fplans. We also encourage people to be
OL,9,Faware of the environmental impacts of
OL,10,Fdroughts as we enter the summer period
OL,11,Fand note the small steps we can all
OL,12,Ftake to save water."
OL,14,FWhat is a drought and what does it
OL,15,Fmean?
OL,17,FThere is no single definition for
OL,18,Fdrought, but it is caused by a period
OL,19,Fof low rainfall.
