OL,6,FThe impacts on people, the
OL,7,Fenvironment, agriculture or business
OL,8,Fwill vary.
OL,10,FSome droughts are short and intense,
OL,11,Fcaused by a hot, dry summer. Others
OL,12,Fare long and take time to develop over
OL,13,Fmultiple seasons due to low amounts of
OL,14,Frainfall.
OL,16,FAll water companies are required to
OL,17,Fhave drought plans and to plan for
OL,18,Freasonable worst-case scenarios.
