OL,6,FThe Environment Agency has moved more
OL,7,Fthan 500 native, white-clawed crayfish
OL,8,Fto a safer location as experts are
OL,9,Fconcerned about water flow in the area.
OL,11,FThere are closures and restrictions in
OL,12,Fplace to preserve water across the
OL,13,FCanal & River Trust network,
OL,14,Fpredominantly on the Leeds & Liverpool
OL,15,FCanal.
OL,17,FPeople are being advised on how to
OL,18,Fsave water, which includes taking
OL,19,Fshorter showers, using water from the
OL,20,Fkitchen to water plants, and fixing
OL,21,Fleaky toilets.
