OL,6,F"The declaration of drought does not
OL,7,Fimmediately change things for our
OL,8,Fcustomers. We'll be continuing to work
OL,9,Fclosely with the Environment Agency
OL,10,Fand will be working hard to carefully
OL,11,Fmanage our resources and move water
OL,12,Faround the region to areas that need
OL,13,Fit most.
OL,15,F"We have 100 additional colleagues
OL,16,Ftackling leakage in the field and we'd
OL,17,Flike to thank customers for continuing
OL,18,Fto report leaks to us so we can repair
OL,19,Fthem as soon as possible."
